ygData.subject: I managed to get my faction..
ygData.msgSnippet: Up high enough with the Paladins in Freeport to not glare at me threateningly.. hehe.. and I m a Dark-elf Shadow Knight.. so.. of course.. the Militia hates my
ygData.messageBody:
Up high enough with the Paladins in Freeport to not glare at me
threateningly.. hehe.. and I'm a Dark-elf Shadow Knight.. so.. of course..
the Militia hates my guts, so I can't even wander the streets of freeport or
go to close to them in East Commons.. and the Two in West COmmons, but
they're push overs now anyway... on another note.. the InnKeepers in East
commons also look at me dubiously now, as opposed to scowl, ready to
attack.. Mind you.. I've killed alot of orcs in East Commons <grin> Though..
I can't go anywhere near the Inns sense the Guards will slaughter me...
hehe.. oh well.. guess I traded off good (look at me dubiously) relation
with the Militia for good <look at me dubiously> relation with the
InnKeepers... ah well...

-The random ramblings of a lvl 17 Tier'dal SK...
